File num_bas_ctrip.nc describe world hydrological basins used in CTRIP, by numbers on grid cells with resolution 0.5°
File rivnum05_new2.txt is the key providing basins name for basin numbers

See
  Decharme, B., Delire, C., Minvielle, M., Colin, J., Vergnes, J. P., Alias, A., et al. (2019).
  Recent Changes in the ISBA-CTRIP Land Surface System for Use in the CNRM-CM6 Climate Model and in Global Off-Line Hydrological Applications.
  J. Adv. Model. Earth Syst. 11, 1207–1252.
  doi:10.1029/2018MS001545.